      "author": "dvdsmpsn (David @ David Simpson Apps)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I’ve seen inbuilt recipe sentences that have a subject and body like so:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/2/32e49ee18f24e2126fd6ff6418c560bb0c5e0cc3.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-10-23 at 16.44.00\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/2/32e49ee18f24e2126fd6ff6418c560bb0c5e0cc3_2_517x348.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-10-23 at 16.44.00\" width=\"517\" height=\"348\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-10-23 at 16.44.00</span><span class=\"informations\">1348×908 57.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>When I add one, the subject line is missing, and the placeholder text isn’t as nice:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/6/a6db187ab0c1a64a9b69ecf253143eb1bbe63fba.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-10-23 at 16.50.27\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/6/a6db187ab0c1a64a9b69ecf253143eb1bbe63fba_2_463x375.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-10-23 at 16.50.27\" width=\"463\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-10-23 at 16.50.27</span><span class=\"informations\">1218×984 54.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>What am I doing wrong?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 207031,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2024-10-24T08:51:39.520Z",
      "author": "dvdsmpsn (David @ David Simpson Apps)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Nm, I used the wrong field type.</p>\n<p>Here’s the correct one (Email):</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/c/4c56f3bcc20197c5718b2d617f31e5462f699108.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-10-24 at 12.45.39\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/c/4c56f3bcc20197c5718b2d617f31e5462f699108_2_412x375.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-10-24 at 12.45.39\" width=\"412\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-10-24 at 12.45.39</span><span class=\"informations\">1398×1270 54.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>And this is what I now get:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/3/e3241153c57e61230e4e4957e5234ba4973d1c0d.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-10-24 at 12.50.05\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/3/e3241153c57e61230e4e4957e5234ba4973d1c0d_2_517x373.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-10-24 at 12.50.05\" width=\"517\" height=\"373\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-10-24 at 12.50.05</span><span class=\"informations\">1282×926 50.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Perfect.</p>"
